3 in Asia, for example, where a lot of the growth is coming from. The opportunity for us is pulling all of the pieces together into a single integrated offering across the full spectrum of clients, and so we've been investing in that platform, the technology. You'll have seen the announcement yesterday in the U.S. about a self-directed digital offering there.

We've been expanding and growing talent in the front line as well. And very pleased as well with the investment product revenue growth, which is -- where from a mix point of view, we see the greatest upside for us. So early days in the execution of this, but I think pleasing progress as we pull this together into this single integrated offering, invest behind it, and you'll see the benefits in terms of growth, as well as obviously return and revenue mix, going forward, for the bank.

